When you were six years old, you wanted
a Lieutenant Neutron action figure.

528
00:33:18,442 --> 00:33:19,770
Lieutenant Neutron?

529
00:33:19,924 --> 00:33:21,260
He was the best!

530
00:33:21,915 --> 00:33:25,567
