531
00:33:26,416 --> 00:33:27,630
Amazing!

532
00:33:28,262 --> 00:33:29,851
Unbelievable.

533
00:33:30,606 --> 00:33:32,594
So what <i>did</i> happen to grandma?

534
00:33:32,642 --> 00:33:34,982
I was makin’ my usual rounds…

535
00:33:35,902 --> 00:33:38,246
On, Donner! On, Dasher!

536
00:33:38,870 --> 00:33:41,354
