go wha-ha!

537
00:33:41,678 --> 00:33:42,820
Wha-ha!

538
00:33:42,950 --> 00:33:44,156
Follow me, guys!

539
00:33:44,614 --> 00:33:45,998
I tried to stop them.

540
00:33:47,500 --> 00:33:48,757
But nothing worked.

541
00:33:49,079 --> 00:33:50,759
Then everything went black.

542
00:33:51,967 --> 00:33:56,099
I’m terribly sorry. I don’t know
what got into those reindeer.

543
00:33:56,668 --> 00:33:57,897
Who are you?

544
00:33:58,436 --> 00:34:01,108
