Quincy!

545
00:34:01,396 --> 00:34:03,590
Leave a note explaining what happened.

546
00:34:04,309 --> 00:34:08,754
So, of course, she was welcome to stay
at the North Pole until she felt better.

547
00:34:09,083 --> 00:34:11,115
