This is a note Santa left at the
accident scene explaining everything.

721
00:44:45,024 --> 00:44:46,833
Dust it for fingerprints.

722
00:44:53,339 --> 00:44:55,189
All right, I admit it.

723
00:44:55,667 --> 00:44:57,450
Yes, yes, I did it.

724
00:44:57,731 --> 00:44:58,794
I hid the note.

725
00:44:59,347 --> 00:45:00,240
And…?

726
00:45:01,215 --> 00:45:04,169
And I made grandpa sign over his rights
to the store.

727
00:45:04,677 --> 00:45:05,511
And…?

728
00:45:05,732 --> 00:45:07,689
I’m behind this evil trial.

729
00:45:07,720 --> 00:45:08,531
And…?

730
00:45:08,890 --> 00:45:11,914
And I hate the goody, goody feelings
of Christmas –

731
00:45:12,203 --> 00:45:14,070
all this caring and sharing.

732
00:45:14,098 --> 00:45:17,268
So I kidnapped grandma and made
Santa Claus the fall guy

733
00:45:17,272 --> 00:45:19,047
so I could get all his money.

734
00:45:19,385 --> 00:45:20,061
Hey,

735
00:45:20,536 --> 00:45:21,907
I deserve to be rich.

736
00:45:21,923 --> 00:45:26,188
Arrest this woman for obstructing justice
and almost ruining Christmas.

737
00:45:26,648 --> 00:45:29,138
That’s what you get for being selfish and stupid.

738
00:45:30,083 --> 00:45:32,110
Babe, you’ll look great in stripes.

739
00:45:32,541 --> 00:45:36,213
Santa Claus, you are hereby found
innocent of all charges.

740
00:45:36,550 --> 00:45:37,883
You are free to go.

