00:46:06,909 --> 00:46:10,067
Young man, after everything
Jake has gone through

747
00:46:10,379 --> 00:46:12,571
do you really think I’m gonna sell?

748
00:46:12,753 --> 00:46:15,392
I don’t want to buy it.
I want to franchise it –

749
00:46:15,496 --> 00:46:18,801
open Spankenheimer general stores
all over the country.

750
00:46:19,077 --> 00:46:21,014
And I want you to be in charge.

751
00:46:21,465 --> 00:46:22,445
You did it.

752
00:46:23,026 --> 00:46:25,042
You’re a pretty cool little bro.

753
