even when the rest of us did.

755
00:46:30,813 --> 00:46:31,710
So, Jake,

756
00:46:32,342 --> 00:46:34,066
what do you want for Christmas?

757
00:46:34,453 --> 00:46:35,327
Nothin’.

758
00:46:35,623 --> 00:46:38,671
I already got the best Christmas gift ever.

759
00:46:39,449 --> 00:46:41,738
I feel the same way.

760
00:46:42,172 --> 00:46:43,995
I’m glad you’re back, grandma.

761
00:46:44,975 --> 00:46:48,319
On, Donner, on, Blitzen…

762
00:46:48,868 --> 00:46:50,078
The rest of you!

763
00:46:53,003 --> 00:46:54,457
Just the way it happened.

764
00:46:54,991 --> 00:46:56,390
Oh, wait.

765
00:46:57,121 --> 00:46:59,275
